Class PGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.util.graph.BaseGraph
      • edu.harvard.util.graph.Graph<PNode,PEdge,PSummaryNode,PGraph>
        • edu.harvard.pass.PGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WithPMeta, java.io.Serializable

    public class PGraph
extends Graph<PNode,PEdge,PSummaryNode,PGraph>
implements java.io.Serializable, WithPMeta
    A provenance graph. It contains nodes of type PNode and edges of type PEdge.
    Author:
    Peter Macko
